[2025-10-31 17:12:41] [OUTPUT] в•”в•ђв•ђв•ђ рџ“„ test_markdown.md (2.7 KB) в•ђв•ђв•ђ\n# uDOS Test Document\n\nThis is a test document for the **uDOS Markdown Viewer** with GitHub-style rendering.\n\n## Features\n\n- вњ… GitHub-flavored markdown\n- вњ… Syntax highlighting\n- вњ… Custom `ucode` language support\n- вњ… Monaspace font integration\n\n## Example uCODE Commands\n\nHere are some example uCODE commands:\n\n```ucode\n[SYSTEM|CLS]\n[SYSTEM|HELP*CATALOG]\n[FILE|LOAD*README.MD*main]\n[FILE|SAVE*main*output.txt]\n[GRID|PANEL*CREATE*workspace]\n[AI|ASK*What is uDOS?*main]\n[MAP|GOTO*10*20]\n[MAP|MOVE*5*-3]\n```\n\n## Command Breakdown\n\n### System Commands\n\n```ucode\n[SYSTEM|CLS]\n```\nClear the screen.\n\n```ucode\n[SYSTEM|HELP*ALL]\n```\nShow help for all commands.\n\n```ucode\n[SYSTEM|REBOOT]\n```\nRestart uDOS with fresh system detection.\n\n### File Operations\n\n```ucode\n[FILE|LOAD*document.md*editor]\n```\nLoad `document.md` into the `editor` panel.\n\n```ucode\n[FILE|SAVE*editor*output.md]\n```\nSave the `editor` panel to `output.md`.\n\n### AI Integration\n\n```ucode\n[AI|ASK*Summarize this document*main]\n```\nAsk Gemini AI to summarize content from the `main` panel.\n\n### Map Navigation\n\n```ucode\n[MAP|GOTO*25*30]\n```\nTeleport to coordinates (25, 30).\n\n```ucode\n[MAP|MOVE*-5*10]\n```\nMove -5 on X axis, +10 on Y axis.\n\n```ucode\n[MAP|LAYER*background]\n```\nSwitch to the `background` layer.\n\n## Code Examples\n\n### Python\n\n```python\ndef hello_udos():\n    print("Welcome to uDOS!")\n    return True\n```\n\n### JavaScript\n\n```javascript\nfunction renderMarkdown(content) {\n    const html = marked.parse(content);\n    return html;\n}\n```\n\n### JSON\n\n```json\n{\n  "SYSTEM_NAME": "uDOS",\n  "VERSION": "1.1",\n  "FEATURES": [\n    "Hybrid Parser",\n    "Themed Lexicon",\n    "AI Integration"\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## Tables\n\n| Command | Module | Description |\n|---------|--------|-------------|\n| CLS | SYSTEM | Clear screen |\n| LOAD | FILE | Load file into panel |\n| ASK | AI | Query Gemini |\n| GOTO | MAP | Teleport to coordinates |\n\n## Task Lists\n\n- [x] Create markdown viewer\n- [x] Add uCODE syntax highlighting\n- [x] Support GitHub styling\n- [ ] Test in multiple browsers\n- [ ] Add custom themes\n\n## Blockquotes\n\n> **uDOS Philosophy:**\n>\n> A hybrid system that translates human-readable commands into structured uCODE,\n> maintaining the 8-bit retro aesthetic while leveraging modern AI capabilities.\n\n## Inline Code\n\nUse `SHOW "README.MD"` to view files in the browser, or `EDIT "config.json"` to edit them directly.\n\n## Horizontal Rule\n\n---\n\n## Links\n\n- [uDOS GitHub](https://github.com/fredporter/uDOS)\n- [Wiki Documentation](https://github.com/fredporter/uDOS/wiki)\n- [Command Reference](https://github.com/fredporter/uDOS/wiki/Command-Reference)\n\n## Images\n\n![uDOS Logo](https://via.placeholder.com/150?text=uDOS)\n\n---\n\n**Test Complete!** рџЋ‰\n\nThis document demonstrates all markdown features including the custom `ucode` syntax highlighting.\n\nв•љв•ђв•ђв•ђ End of test_markdown.md в•ђв•ђв•ђ\n
